DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-08-08T03:30:00&endDate=2026-08-10T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nBAKERLOO LINE: Saturday 8 and Sunday 9 August\, no service between Queens Park and Harrow & Wealdstone. There will also be no LIONESS LINE service between Euston and Watford Junction. Use LONDON NORTHWESTERN RAILWAY services between Euston and Harrow & Wealdstone\, or SOUTHERN services\, where available\, between Wembley Central and Harrow & Wealdstone. Special bus service 718 operates between Queens Park and Harrow & Wealdstone via Kensal Green\, Willesden Junction (Harrow Road)\, Harlesden (Jubilee Clock / Manor Park Road)\, Stonebridge Park (Harrow Road)\, Wembley Central (Park Lane and Station)\, North Wembley\, Preston Road (for Metropolitan line and South Kenton) and Kenton.
